trans-unit.source: Specifies a print controller that sends information to a printer.
trans-unit.target: Angir en trykt kontroller som sender informasjon til en skriver.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintDocument> uses this class.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintDocument>bruker denne klassen.</xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintDocument>

trans-unit.source: For more information on printing, see the <xref:System.Drawing.Printing> namespace overview.
trans-unit.target: Du finner mer informasjon om utskrift av <xref:System.Drawing.Printing>Oversikt over navneområde.</xref:System.Drawing.Printing>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Drawing.Printing.StandardPrintController"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Drawing.Printing.StandardPrintController"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: Completes the control sequence that determines when and how to print a page of a document.
trans-unit.target: Fullfører kontrollen sekvensen som bestemmer når og hvordan du skriver ut en side med et dokument.

trans-unit.source: OnEndPage is called immediately after the <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintDocument> raises the <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintDocument.PrintPage> event.
trans-unit.target: OnEndPage kalles like etter den <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintDocument>opphøyer den <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintDocument.PrintPage>hendelsen.</xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintDocument.PrintPage> </xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintDocument>

trans-unit.source: If an exception is thrown inside a <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintDocument.PrintPage> event of a <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintDocument>, OnEndPage is not called.
trans-unit.target: Hvis det et unntak i en <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintDocument.PrintPage>hendelse for en <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintDocument>, OnEndPage ikke kalles.</xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintDocument> </xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintDocument.PrintPage>

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.StandardPrintController.OnStartPrint%2A> creates the <xref:System.Drawing.Graphics> object that is sent to the printer.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.StandardPrintController.OnStartPrint%2A>oppretter den <xref:System.Drawing.Graphics>objekt som er sendt til skriveren.</xref:System.Drawing.Graphics></xref:System.Drawing.Printing.StandardPrintController.OnStartPrint%2A>

trans-unit.source: After <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.StandardPrintController.OnStartPrint%2A> is called, the <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.StandardPrintController.OnStartPage%2A> method sets the <xref:System.Drawing.Graphics> object to a graphic of a single page.
trans-unit.target: Etter <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.StandardPrintController.OnStartPrint%2A>kalles, den <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.StandardPrintController.OnStartPage%2A>metoden angir den <xref:System.Drawing.Graphics>objektet som et bilde av én side.</xref:System.Drawing.Graphics> </xref:System.Drawing.Printing.StandardPrintController.OnStartPage%2A> </xref:System.Drawing.Printing.StandardPrintController.OnStartPrint%2A>

trans-unit.source: The OnEndPage method clears the <xref:System.Drawing.Graphics> object, while the <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.StandardPrintController.OnEndPrint%2A> method deallocates the object.
trans-unit.target: OnEndPage-metoden fjerner den <xref:System.Drawing.Graphics>objektet mens den <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.StandardPrintController.OnEndPrint%2A>metoden opphever tildeling objektet.</xref:System.Drawing.Printing.StandardPrintController.OnEndPrint%2A> </xref:System.Drawing.Graphics>

trans-unit.source: When OnEndPage is called from a printing context of a <xref:System.Windows.Forms.PrintDialog> a <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintingPermission> of <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintingPermissionLevel> is required.
trans-unit.target: Når OnEndPage kalles fra en utskrift konteksten for en <xref:System.Windows.Forms.PrintDialog>en <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintingPermission>av <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintingPermissionLevel>kreves.</xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintingPermissionLevel> </xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintingPermission> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.PrintDialog>

trans-unit.source: Printing to the default printer requires a <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintingPermission> of <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintingPermissionLevel>.
trans-unit.target: Standard-skriveren krever en <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintingPermission>av <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintingPermissionLevel>.</xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintingPermissionLevel> </xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintingPermission>

trans-unit.source: All other calls this method requires a <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintingPermission> of <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintingPermissionLevel>
trans-unit.target: Alle andre kall denne metoden krever en <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintingPermission>av <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintingPermissionLevel></xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintingPermissionLevel> </xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintingPermission>
